item.title: CVE-2023-3438|2024-08-02T06:55:03.399Z -- trellix -- trellix%20move
item.description: An unquoted Windows search path vulnerability existed in the install the MOVE 4.10.x and earlier Windows install service (mvagtsce.exe). The misconfiguration allowed an unauthorized local user to insert arbitrary code into the unquoted service path to obtain privilege escalation and stop antimalware services.
